    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "（うぅぅ……眠たい……）\n（数学の授業って、どうしてこんなに眠くなるんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ugh…… I'm sleepy……）\n（Why is math class so sleepy）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "（寝ちゃダメ、寝ちゃダメ……）\n（寝ちゃ……ダメ………………）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Don't sleep‚ don't sleep…）\n（Don't… sleep………）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7329479535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.6005220985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん、渚……\nさっきの授業のノート、写させてくれない……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ Nagisa…\nCan I copy your notes from the previous lesson…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6571882565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.4551486014
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ちらって見たけど、やっぱり寝ちゃってたんだ\nでもめずらしいね。寝不足？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ I had a quick look‚ you were sleeping as expected\nBut that's unusual. Lack of sleep?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4551486014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.6596613565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと寝てはいるんだけど、眠りが浅いのかしら……\nよく夢を見るの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sleeping well‚ but am I just sleeping lightly…\nI dream often",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6596613565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.9864664394
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "どんな夢？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What dream?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9864664394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.6789138752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "……お姉ちゃんの夢。気づいたら小学生に戻っててね\n二人で、お母さんのピアノに合わせて歌ってるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…My sister's dream. When I realized it‚ we're back in elementary school\nand we're singing along to mother's piano",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6789138752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.6613399782
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "素敵だね\n夢に見るくらい、大切な思い出なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's nice\nIt must be a precious memory‚ enough to dream about",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.6613399782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.0432221053
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね\n何気ないことだったけど、大切だったのかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right\nIt's a trivial thing‚ but it's important",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0432221053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.1855804084
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、いいな～。私も琴乃ちゃんの夢に出てみたい\nオーディションはいつでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ it's nice~. I want to appear in Kotono's dream‚ too\nWhen is the audition?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1855804084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.7356711665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "オーディションって……。ドラマじゃないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Auditions…. It's not a drama",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.6988230823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　絶対楽しいのに。……そうだ！　写真を枕の下\nに入れると、その人の夢を見るって言わない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~? It must be fun. …Right! There's a saying that if you put a photo\nunder your pillow‚ you'll dream of that person?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6988230823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.0333356221
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.9343104798
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "先に言っておくけど、やらないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For your information‚ I won't do it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9343104798,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
