    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "（ふぁ……そろそろ寝ないと……）\n（……あれ、渚からメッセ……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Fuwa… I should go to sleep‚ soon…）\n（…Oh‚ a message from Nagisa…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.5066007415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 105.8697980363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "『琴乃ちゃん、私の写真を送るね\n二人でお空の雲をもぐもぐ食べる夢がいいな～』……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Kotono-chan‚ I'll send you my photo\nI want to dream that we munching on the clouds in the sky together~\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8697980363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "（確かに、雲を食べるなんて夢でしか出来ないけど……）\n（ちょっとファンシー過ぎるような……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Of course‚ eating clouds is something that only happens in dreams…）\n（It's a bit too fancy…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4312036633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.3332215428
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_ktn_01_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、渚の写真なんていっぱい持ってるし\n夢にだって……。もぉ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the first place‚ I have a lot of photos of Nagisa\nEven in my dreams…. Often….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3332215428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
